name: isaxvelte-pro
description: Use Iconsax icons in Svelte applications.
readme:
# Iconsax for Svelte This is an icon library for Svelte based on [iconsax](https://iconsax.io/). These icons are adapted to inherit the colors and sizes, you can use it as if it were a letter font. Take advantage of [Sveltekit](https://kit.svelte.dev) to be able to use the icons from [iconsax](https://iconsax.io/) with Isaxvelte-Pro ğŸ˜ğŸ‘Œ.
Ver preview Isaxvelte-Pro
